# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [1.1.0] - 2026-03-13
### Added
- Functional de-duplication logic using JavaScript `Set` in `contentScript.js`.
- URL validation to ensure only `http` and `https` protocols are captured.
- Added `target="_blank"` and `rel="noopener"` to dumped links for better UX and security.
- Popup-blocker detection with user alert.

### Changed
- Updated `manifest.json` version from 1.0 to 1.1.
- Refactored `contentScript.js` for better readability and performance.
- Improved CSS styling in the output table for a more modern "dark mode" look.

### Fixed
- Issue where duplicate URLs from the same page filled the dump list.
- Broken links caused by empty `href` attributes or internal anchors.

